item.title: Today I Learnt
item.description: As hard and fast as modern life is, I think that it’s important to take time out of your schedule and make sure that you keep regular contact with friends. I like to think that I’m better than most at this. I do overthink the reasons why people don’t reciprocate this, but hey. People.
